data.description: Adorable Bungalow Home!!  This very clean, crisp, and modern 3 bed, 2 bath home has beautiful hardwood floors, new carpet in the bedrooms, freshly painted interior, and newer stone countertops. The finished attic area adds an additional 377 sq ft of finished living space for a large master bedroom, family room, office, or playroom...your choice!  There is also a ton of separate storage space up there on both sides of the room. The large back yard is fully fenced in and leads right into the detached garage.  The garage is large enough to park a vehicle and have extra room to work on things and store your mower. There is also additional parking on the back side of the fence beside the garage. Don’t miss out on this adorable place, call your realtor today!!  You can take a virtual tour now by watching the video!!
